Name: Discard Room
FirstTimeDescription: This is the Discard Room, a cramped and eerie space filled with the stench of decay.
Description: You find yourself in a small, cramped room. Harsh, flickering fluorescent lights reveal peeling paint and rusted metal surfaces.; A large, ominous garbage chute dominates one wall, a corpse is crumpled on the floor, and a small door leads back to the hallway.

Interactables.Name: Garbage Chute
Interactables.Description: A massive, dark garbage chute looms ominously on one wall. It seems big enough to dispose of something significant.
